ef":"1Sam.3.1","text":"And the child Samuel ministered unto the LORD before Eli. And the word of the LORD was precious in those days; there was no open vision.","year":-1165},{"id":"recztbmXlxCTouZCO","ref":"1Sam.3.2","text":"And it came to pass at that time, when Eli was laid down in his place, and his eyes began to wax dim, that he could not see;","year":-1165},{"id":"recrI4i1laHjYz2Ku","ref":"1Sam.3.3","text":"And ere the lamp of God went out in the temple of the LORD, where the ark of God was, and Samuel was laid down to sleep;","year":-1165},{"id":"rec1gwoTpvgCDnumx","ref":"1Sam.3.4","text":"That the LORD called Samuel: and he answered, Here am I.","year":-1165},{"id":"recYb3ON5ia2R5aiC","ref":"1Sam.3.5","text":"And he ran unto Eli, and said, Here am I; for thou calledst me. And he said, I called not; lie down again. And he went and lay down.","year":-1165},{"id":"recm9mh4JH3xtSSer","ref":"1Sam.3.6","text":"And the LORD called yet again, Samuel. And Samuel arose and went to Eli, and said, Here am I; for thou didst call me. And he answered, I called not, my son; lie down again.","year":-1165},{"id":"reclmStFu8YN0NORP","ref":"1Sam.3.7","text":"Now Samuel did not yet know the LORD, neither was the word of the LORD yet revealed unto him.","year":-1165},{"id":"recN6cANKS6BONQh1","ref":"1Sam.3.8","text":"And the LORD called Samuel again the third time. And he arose and went to Eli, and said, Here am I; for thou didst call me. And Eli perceived that the LORD had called the child.","year":-1165}]}
